  "body": "I would like it if we could just use the same URI for both JSON RPC and WebSocket.\r\n\r\nGeth simply exposes one port and path\r\n\r\nNethermind has 1 port and 2 paths\r\n\r\nI'm not sure there's really a need to have the extra `/ws/json-rpc` path at the end of the URI? Is there?\r\n\r\nNot very important, but it is a minor annoyance.",
